    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been reliably maintained. The engine runs smoothly, and the interior is clean with only minor wear on the driver's seat and floor mats. While the exterior paint still shines, you may find a few small stone chips on the hood and light scratches near the door handles from normal use. It\u2019s a dependable car that is ready for daily driving without any immediate major service needs.",
      "price": 34500.0,
